---
title: Ras El Hanout Beef Strips & Carrot Couscous with Tomato & Mint Salsa
description: How satisfying are juicy beef strips on a bed of fluffy carrot couscous? You'll have to make this delectable ras el hanout-spiced
dish to find out! We've added cooling mint salsa and creamy yoghurt to top it off. Simply delicious.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chermoula-beef-strips-carrot-couscous-2b43ea64.jpg
